OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and dry evening but with the
OL,7,Fodd isolated shower possible. Cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with any showers becoming
OL,9,Fconfined to western Tayside and
OL,10,FCentral areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA mainly dry bright day with
OL,13,Fsome sunny spells breaking through,
OL,14,Fthough there could be a light morning
OL,15,Fshower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
