OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,7,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,8,FPlenty of warm sunny spells, but often
OL,9,Fcloudier, cooler near the coast.
OL,10,FPatchy overnight frost.
